node.text:
This is my real. It’s not glamorous. It’s full of messes, feeding, working, tidy-ing, rocking, wiping, & melt downs...I set out to do this to show you the reality of what my life looks like, and I ended up with six minutes of footage that I’ll treasure forever. Sometimes it’s not till we take a step back and watch, that we truly see all the work we’ve done, & most days I feel like I haven’t actually ACCOMPLISHED one task. But I have cared for and LOVED these tiny humans well, and that is my greatest accomplishment. I hope that watching it makes YOU proud, mama. This is mom life, and I’ll take the crazy over the glamorous any day - it’s the greatest job I could ever have. 
Thank you @mayavorderstrasse for  inspiring me to capture the REAL. 👊🏼
